(1, '<p>同时多个选择器执行同一个setInterval：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>函数内:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var that=this;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>setInteval(function(){</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">that...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>//that前一定要用var，否则都指向到最后一个了</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>xxx</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-06-13 10:26:51', '2016-08-07 02:23:27'),
(2, '<p><strong><span style="color:#FF0000;">gulpfile.js</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 500px;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">.pipe($.clean({force:true}));</span></td>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">.pipe($.replace());</span></td>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">.pipe($.rename());</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">.pipe($.concat());</span></td>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">.pipe($.wrap());</span></td>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">.pipe($.ngmin());</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">.pipe($.size());</span></td>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">.pipe($.rjs2());</span></td>\r\n			<td><span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">gulp.run()</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#EE82EE;"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">$.runSequence()执行gulp时建议用依赖关系或gulp.watch()代替</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#EE82EE;"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">$.rjs2：</span>https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-rjs2</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>--<span style="color:#FF0000;"><strong>SourceTree</strong></span>只是git的操作UI，首先得安装有git</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--SourceTree提交失败提示set <span style="color:#B22222;">git config</span>，解决如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>打开&lsquo;Git Bash&rsquo;命令行</li>\r\n	<li>$&nbsp;git&nbsp;config&nbsp;--global&nbsp;user.name&nbsp;&quot;flora&quot;&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>$&nbsp;git&nbsp;config&nbsp;--global&nbsp;user.email&nbsp;123.com</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>如想查看已有配置，命令如下：$ git config --list</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--SourceTree再重新提交，OK</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>--<span style="color:#B22222;">node.js</span>安装：官网https://nodejs.org/en/download/下载，直接安装</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--要安装模块，貌似要先点开一下安装目录的&#39;npm.cmd&#39;文件</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--cmd里安装<span style="color:#B22222;">gulp</span>到全局：npm install gulp -g</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#EE82EE;">--要在指定目录使用gulp,把gulp安装到该目录：<span style="font-size: 13.3333339691162px;">npm install gulp</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>--cmd里安装模块到指定目录如：d: -&gt; cd AppServwww -&gt; npm install gulp-less --save dev</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; (安装gulp-less等了很久，最后直接把命令行管理，但gulpfile使用此模块没问题)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; <span style="color:#EE82EE;">(在家安装时很快，但报错与操作系统不兼容，生成npm-debug文件，但还是安装了不影响使用)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; （安装gulp-minify-css时提示&#39;Please use gulp-clean-css&#39;）,但不影响使用</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>gulp-load-plugins模块：在gulpfile.js里用它来自动加载package.json力的插件（用到时才加载）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--var $=require(&#39;gulp-load-plugins&#39;)();</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--如使用gulp-less插件时不需要再less = require(&#39;gulp-less&#39;)，调用时直接用$.less就好</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--$.后的命名：插件名去掉&#39;gulp-&#39;，必要时再转驼峰,如：gulp-minify-css 写成 $.minifyCss</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--gulpfile.js不需要调入package.json,但保证其在同目录上，保证用到的gulp插件都列举在内</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>多个项目的gulpfile.js共用一个/node_modules：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--npm install fbi &gt;&gt; 此模块会在当前目录生成mode_modules的引用? 和package.json文件</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; （https://www.npmjs.com/package/fbi/tutorial）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; （一般的gulp模块没问题，但测试中gulp-load-plugins提示找不到）</p>\r\n', 'red', '2016-06-14 07:26:22', '2016-06-19 02:33:16'),
(3, '<p>requirejs各页面通用配置实现（两方法应该是等价的）：</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width:500px;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="line-height:16px;">方法一：</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="line-height:16px;">&lt;script src=&quot;js/require.js&quot; data-main=&quot;p_index.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="line-height:16px;">&lt;script src=&quot;js/rconfig.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>reconfig.js代码：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 16px; margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">require.config({</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;baseUrl:&#39;js&#39;,</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;paths:{</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;jq&quot;:&quot;lib/jquery-1.10.2&quot;,</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;common&quot;:&quot;app/common&quot;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">});</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#EE82EE;">测试加载p_index.js时rconfig.js已加载符合要求，但以防rconfig.js比较大时可能不会先与p_index.js加载以致不能预先配置，最后还是建议用方法二</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width:500px;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="line-height:16px;">方法二：</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="line-height:16px;">&lt;script src=&quot;scripts/rconfig.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">&lt;script src=&quot;js/require.js&quot; data-main=&quot;p_index.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>rconfig.js代码：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 16px; margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">function(window){</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;var require={</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;baseUrl:&#39;js&#39;,</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;paths:{</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;jq&quot;:&quot;lib/jquery-1.10.2&quot;,</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;common&quot;:&quot;app/common&quot;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;}</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">}(window);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>p_index.js代码（两方法一样）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 16px; margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">(function(){</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;require([&#39;common&#39;],function(){</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;console.log(&quot;首页&quot;); &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;})</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">});</span></p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-06-15 02:39:48', '2016-08-07 02:21:38'),
(5, '<p><strong><span style="color:#B22222;"><span style="font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">gulp.src的base属性</span></span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">gulp.src(script</span><span class="hljs-regexp" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">/lib/</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">*.js) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//没有配置base参数，此时默认的base路径为script/lib</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> </span><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//假设匹配到的文件为script/lib/jquery.js</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> .pipe(gulp.dest(</span><span class="hljs-string" style="color: rgb(163, 21, 21); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">&#39;build&#39;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">)) </span><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//生成的文件路径为 build/jquery.js</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">gulp.src(script</span><span class="hljs-regexp" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">/lib/</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">*.js, {</span><span class="hljs-string" style="color: rgb(163, 21, 21); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">base:</span><span class="hljs-string" style="color: rgb(163, 21, 21); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">&#39;script&#39;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">}) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//配置了base参数，此时base路径为script</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> </span><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//假设匹配到的文件为script/lib/jquery.js</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> .pipe(gulp.dest(</span><span class="hljs-string" style="color: rgb(163, 21, 21); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">&#39;build&#39;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">)) </span><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//此时生成的文件路径为 build/lib/jquery.js </span></p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-06-15 07:49:51', '2016-08-07 02:20:40'),
(4, '<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width:600px;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style="line-height: 16px;">gulp-requirejs-optimize：</span></td>\r\n			<td><span style="line-height: 16px;">--</span>把require的脚本文件包含其所有依赖一起合并压缩</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>--通过exclude把不需要一起合并的共用文件排除</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">//合并压缩js<br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">gulp.task(&#39;scripts&#39;, function () {</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp; &nbsp; return gulp.src([&#39;resource_pre/js/*.js&#39;,&#39;!resource_pre/js/require.js&#39;])</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(requirejsOptimize(function(file) {</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return {</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;exclude: [</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;lib/jquery-1.10.2.js&quot;,</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&#39;layout/common.js&#39;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;]</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;};</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}))</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(gulp.dest(&#39;resource/js&#39;));</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">});</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-06-15 05:50:32', '2016-08-07 02:20:36'),
(6, '<p>github</p>\r\n\r\n<p>为什么要用代理：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>http://www.tuicool.com/articles/ZrENby</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>代理proxy Server的作用：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>http://wenwen.sogou.com/z/q99783124.htm</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-06-15 14:52:24', '2016-08-07 02:18:41'),
(7, '<p><span style="color:#B22222;"><strong>git：</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>安装了TortoiseGit2.1.0.0-64bit.msi(附带有TortoiseGit-LanguagePack-2.1.0.0-64bit-zh_CN.msi)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--创建版本库 ； 可通过把目录中的.git隐藏文件删掉可取消git对此目录的控制</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--Git克隆等每次都需要输入账号密码，保存此些信息不需重复输入的方法：</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>cmd中输入&#39;%USERPROFILE%&#39; 回车会打开根目录</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>新建&#39;_netrc&#39;文件</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>输入以下信息ctrl+z保存</p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>\r\n		<p>machine github.com //git服务器名称，如 &#39;machine localhost&#39;</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n		<p>login username</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n		<p>password password</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#B22222;">Clover工具</span></strong>：&#39;我的电脑&#39;增加多标签页的功能，方便同时查看/操作多个不同路径的文件夹，支持快捷键与标签页的拖入拖出</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'grey', '2016-06-16 08:42:54', '2016-08-10 19:47:12'),
(8, '<p>--开发block库，复制功能：展示/copy css/copy html/copy all，可选择性合并生成</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--ie的filter滤镜</p>\r\n', 'black', '2016-06-16 09:00:05', '2016-08-07 02:14:30'),
(9, '<p>js获取文件创建,最后修改,最后访问时间：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);">DateCreated、DateLastModified、DateLastAccessed</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">var fso = new ActiveXObject(&quot;Scripting.FileSystemObject&quot;);&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;var f1 = fso.GetFile(&quot;d: est.txt&quot;);&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;alert(&quot;File last modified: &quot; + f1.DateLastModified);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">jq获取当前文档的最后修改时间：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="color: rgb(19, 19, 19); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 宋体, 微软雅黑, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24.05px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);">document.write(&quot;本页最后更新日期: &quot; + document.lastModified + &quot;&quot;)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>php获取文档时间信息：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">$a=filemtime(&quot;log.txt&quot;);</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">echo &quot;修改时间：&quot;.date(&quot;Y-m-d H:i:s&quot;,$a).&quot;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><font color="#4b4b4b" face="Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">//</span></font><span style="color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">filemtime:上次被修改的时间</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">//filectime:上次 inode 被修改的时间</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">//fileatime:文件上次被访问的时间</span></p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-06-17 03:06:37', '2016-08-07 02:13:38'),
(10, '<p>创建touch <strong><span style="color:#B22222;">.gitignore</span></strong>(提交时忽略的文件配置)：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>右键 -&gt;&nbsp;选Git Bash -&gt;&nbsp;输入 touch .gitignore</p>\r\n\r\n<p>共享模式：&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;过滤文件夹：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">/mtk/</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;指定过滤某种类型的文件：<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">*.zip</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">*.rar</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;指定过滤某个文件：<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">/mtk/if.h</span><br />\r\n保守模式：<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;跟踪某个文件夹：<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">!/plutommi/mmi</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;跟踪某类文件：<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">!*.c</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">!*.h</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;跟踪某个指定文件：<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#FFFFE0;">!/plutommi/mmi/mmi_features.h</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>原则：一个文件夹下有很多文件夹和文件，而我只想跟踪其中的一个文件，这样设置就可以满足这种情况，先用共享模式把整个目录 都设置为不跟踪，然后再用保守模式把这个文件夹中想要跟踪的文件设置为被跟踪，配置很简单，就可以跟踪想要跟踪的文件。</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-06-17 09:29:39', '2016-08-07 02:12:17'),
(11, '<p>--测试都使用ip访问</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--git提交记住勾选作者和时间</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--任何信息都是有用的，多想一步</p>\r\n', 'black', '2016-06-28 13:14:41', '2016-08-07 02:10:57'),
(13, '<p>--网页顶部莫名出现空行，是由于采用utf-8编码时自动为网页添加BOM签名，DW里设编码的时候取消&ldquo;包括unicode签名（BOM）&rdquo;的勾选</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--utf-8 BOM的问题也会导致如压缩下载等报错&#39;cannot modify header information - headers already sent by (.)&#39;</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-07-04 02:44:35', '2016-08-07 02:10:29'),
(14, '<p>cmd -&gt; npm install 把package.json中的模块安装到该目录新建的node-modules文件夹下</p>\r\n\r\n<p>（cmd执行后停在一个地方很久，但模块使用不受影响）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-07-05 07:12:47', '2016-08-07 02:09:21'),
(15, '<p>requirejsOptimize模块会安装mainConfigFile配置文件和依赖关系合并文件，参数exclude排除不要被合并的文件，如src中不用&#39;!&#39;排除此些文件，将会对用生成一个空文件到dest目录</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-07-06 02:39:45', '2016-08-07 02:09:27'),
(16, '<p>--Sublime Text自带的代码格式化：<span style="color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 21.06px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Edit - Line - Reindent（编辑 - 行 - 再次缩进）</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>--box-sizing(+webkit+moz)兼容到ie8</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--.flex用的也是box-sizing</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-07-07 01:22:29', '2016-08-07 02:09:33'),
(17, '<p>用镜像提升npm模块安装速度：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--定制cnpm命令行工具代替默认的npm:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">$ npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>--用此来安装某模块：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">$ cnpm install gulp-jade</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>--用此来安装package全部模块：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">$ cnpm install</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>--同步某模块：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">$ cnpm sync gulp-plumber</span></p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-07-08 05:41:33', '2016-08-07 02:04:30'),
(18, '<p>直接在浏览器打开js文件有时中文会乱码，用dw打开设置编码utf-8及勾选下面&#39;BOM&#39;就不乱码了</p>\r\n', 'green', '2016-07-10 08:29:13', '2016-08-07 02:02:54'),
